# NOTE: DATABASE_URL is NOT used as a Docker secret in this stack.
# The backend assembles the URL at startup from POSTGRES_HOST / PORT / USER /
# DB (plain env) plus POSTGRES_PASSWORD (file-mounted secret). Keep only
# `postgres_password` and `session_secret` files under secrets/.
#
# This file is here purely as a placeholder so the directory documents that
# DATABASE_URL is deliberately not a secret in this stack.
